Comment: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:52.00,Dialogue,chapters,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Această voce...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.96,0:01:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.62,0:01:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lay low in here for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this!?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, așa te comporți cu cele care îți ling acadeaua?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vă implor, țineți-vă gura închisă!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.93,0:01:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peter!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.06,0:02:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bună dimineața, Luvellia...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.85,0:02:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peter!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai, c-ce s-a întâmplat?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.41,0:02:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sweating up a storm!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-About that...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.87,0:02:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Training!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup, I was in the middle of my training routine!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.19,0:02:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maintaining a strict regimen rather than allowing\Nyour accomplishments to inflate your ego...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.01,0:02:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why you are suited\Nto become my husband.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-senpai...?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a reason I've come to see you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we return to Guild Headquarters today...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I plan on informing my father of our engagement.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll lend me your support, won't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, you're the only woman I've got eyes for!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I entered the tournament for a chance\Nto earn her hand in marriage.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting the green light from the Guildmaster\Nwould be a perfect ending to our story...!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Denied.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Father...!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were so enthusiastic about the idea of the
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grand Fighting Tournament Champion\Nbecoming your son-in-law!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peter Grill!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attempting to deceive my daughter, are you!?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your death shall be swift!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.86,0:03:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you cannot accept the reality of our relationship,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am prepared to cut ties with you\Nand move away from home!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous...!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.17,0:03:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A life without my precious Luvellia...!?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have come to this decision of my own accord.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's done for...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.73,0:03:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it appears I've been left with no choice\Nbut to grant you my blessing...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mark my words, Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.28,0:04:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will {\i1}rue{\i0} this day!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You impudent, conniving...!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let it be known:
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Guild hereby recognizes the engagement\Nbetween Peter Grill and Lady Luvellia!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.60,0:04:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make preparations for a feast in their honor,\Nand to celebrate our triumph in the tournament!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm surprised you managed\Nto convince the Guildmaster...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I was quite nervous.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've seen for yourself how ruthless my father can be.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.53,0:04:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was my faith in you that gave\Nme the strength to confront him.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.38,0:04:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that she trusts me so deeply...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guilt is eating me alive...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If word got out about my fling with the Ogre sisters,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Guildmaster would wring my neck...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if Luvellia-senpai somehow found out...!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.22,0:05:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kinda late, but we wanna sincerely congratulate\Nyou on goin' public with your engagement!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, we shall cheer you on from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must've had a change of heart...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that note, Senpai...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hopin' to get a big ol' batch\Nof baby batter again tonight...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y'mind if we bump uglies right here?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.26,0:05:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who in the world wouldn't mind!?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look... You heard the news, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm officially engaged to Luvellia-senpai now...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.68,0:05:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This poses no risk to our objective.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We merely wish to conceive a child\Nwith the world's strongest warrior.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A relationship born of convenience and\Ndevoid of affection is more than adequate.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're insane...!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oopsie!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's make a deal, Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We promise never to disclose\Nthis little arrangement of ours.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.63,0:06:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In return, you shall continue to\Nsupply us with your sweet seed
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.05,0:06:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until we've sucessfully become pregnant... at the least!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those footsteps...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-senpai!?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time to put on pants!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's my next move...!?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little farther...!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peter-kun?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sure was quick...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father was having another one of his outbursts.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the Guildmaster gets angry,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're just about the only one who can calm him down.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish to speak with Luvellia.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.15,0:07:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lend me your seat, won't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was totally unprepared for\Nsomething like this to happen...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving up my seat is the obvious answer.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd catch sight of the naked Ogre sisters...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.26,0:07:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone would realize that my junk's been\Nflappin' in the wind this whole time...!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father! I shall accompany you somewhere private...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.43,0:07:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! Stay right where you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.78,0:07:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you didn't hear me, Peter-kun...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What now...!?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do!?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be some way out of this, right!?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot do!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.47,0:08:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run that by me again.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you just refuse an order?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.79,0:08:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of giving up\Nmy place at Senpai's side...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consider this proof of my commitment to her!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Peter-kun!?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Insolent brat!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.84,0:08:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trying to sway my darling Luvellia\Nwith your empty words again, are you!?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Am I busted!?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Papa?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I get bigger, I'm gonna be your wife!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you cannot accept our relationship,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am prepared to cut ties with you\Nand move away from home!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\bord1.8\shad.8\fade(0,660)\frz352.9\pos(903.465,838.133)}I am prepared to cut ties with you\Nand move away from home!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How loathsome!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I require more alcohol to endure this wretched party...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did he take the bait...?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never had anyone stand up to\Nmy father like that before.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.45,0:09:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This merely reinforces my belief that you're the\Nonly man fit to become my husband.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boop!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Peter-kun?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one for me, Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father's lost his temper again...!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.93,0:09:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.11,0:09:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close...!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.04,0:09:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peekaboo!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like that pesky distraction is finally gone...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Quit stickin' your head out of my crotch!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let us continue.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard what I said back there, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-senpai is the one and only woman I love!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're crazy if you think I'll make\Nanother mistake with the two of you!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.04,0:10:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might claim to have an iron will,\Nbut your downstairs brain suggests otherwise.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A physiological response like this has nothing to do with–
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.74,0:10:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long 'til you start singin' a different tune?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to find out... Senpai.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-senpai has faith in me, of all people...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made the same damn mistake...!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.59,0:10:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are people only capable of rational thought\N{\i1}after{\i0} they've already screwed up...?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te-am găsit... Peter Grill.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dragul meu Peter Grill,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congrats on going public with your engagement!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luvellia-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must be happy as a clam right about now, eh?
