Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:18.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.6}M-am băgat într-o gaură fără cale de scăpare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3)\c&HDEE4E7&\3c&H677077&\move(960,1040,664,1040,6,1386)}Pus cu spatele la zid...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HD1C9C4&\3c&H8C4665&\move(760,1040,1068,1044,111,1151)}Adică, cum aș putea rezista?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:26.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H7D3F9E&}"Asta nu ar fi trebuit să se întâmple",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H7D3F9E&\t(461,920,\c&H313633&\3c&HDBDED5&)}continui să spun în negare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur4\c&H744A4E&\3c&H190D0F&}Mi-aș dori să dispar pur și simplu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:30.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HB2D1F5&\3c&H7657C3&}Mi-aș dori să dispar pur și simplu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:30.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\blur4\c&HD2DDE0&\3c&H5A6167&}Mi-aș dori să dispar pur și simplu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)\c&HF2FCFA&\3c&H5A6167&}Nu mă mai suport
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H453572&}Moping around, spouting lies, grieving a broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:40.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H453572&}I hold on desperately to these feelings and shut my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H84514E&\c&HFFF8F2&}Deci de ce nu vrea {\alpha&HFF&\t(1206,1206,\fs89)\t(1456,1456,\fs98)\t(1748,1748,\fs107)\t(2082,2082,\fs116)\t(2332,2332,\fs125)\t(2583,2583,\fs134)}vina {\alpha&H00&\fs80}asta stupidă să dispară?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H84514E&\c&HFFF8F2&\alpha&HFF&\t(2958,3417,\frz720)\move(960,1060,1760,460,2958,3417)}Deci de ce nu vrea {\alpha&H00&\t(1206,1206,\fs89)\t(1456,1456,\fs98)\t(1748,1748,\fs107)\t(2082,2082,\fs116)\t(2332,2332,\fs125)\t(2583,2583,\fs134)}vina {\alpha&HFF&\fs80}asta stupidă să dispară?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:47.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HB20F81&}Mă sufoc sub greutatea ei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HB20F81&}Șansa de a fi erou s-a dus de mult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H8061BD&}Always discouraged by my weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H8061BD&}I drop to my knees and grovel at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H8061BD&}clinging selfishly to the hope for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:04.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H3B6270&\c&HF1FDFF&}Dug myself into a hole with no way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:07.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3)\3c&HD200C2&}Full of regret and powerless to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H645D99&}I feel my heart being torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H645D99&}on this night of endless shame and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H645D99&}Why can't I get my act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H636F66&\t(926,1259,\3c&H8186B3&)}Got nothing but this pathetic self of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H6F9D73&\blur4\t(\3c&H928974&)}It started out as a simple crush
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Suddenly, you were my biggest source of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Till death do us part, let's grow old together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:04.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}This is my sincerest wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\t(1822,2573,\3c&H67586A&)}So long time, by my side for all eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H67586A&}Beaten down by our daily struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H67586A&}Or soaked by a storm of rage;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H67586A&}If you get drenched, I won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H67586A&}To be the umbrella that shields you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H67586A&}It's not so cold... I'm by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H67586A&}That's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}That smile of yours puts my soul at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}I could search the whole world over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}And find no one like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Just the sight of you fills my heart with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}No matter how much it may hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}I pledge my life to protecting you
